1. Install Frameworks & SQL Express LocalDb
2. Create Directory in wwwroot
3. Create Website and point it to the Directory, Set AppPool to asp.net 4.0
4. Create Application and point to directory
5. Drop Files into directory
6. change application language to c#
7. add .cshtml to mime types
8. run: %windir%\Microsoft.NET\Framework64\v4.0.30319\aspnet_regii.exe -ir
9. Modify C:\Windows\System32\inetsrv\config\applicationHost.config - refer to this blog
 http://rsuharta.wordpress.com/2012/10/19/provider-sql-network-interfaces-error-50-local-database-runtime-error-occurred-cannot-create-an-automatic-instance-see-the-windows-application-event-log-for-error-details/